    "question_id" : 4778113,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I just fixed this by reselecting a default JRE for the execution environment (JRE6 for JavaSE-1.6 in my case). It got unchecked for some reason.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 374335,
      "reputation" : 4225,
