    "creation_date" : 1336155021,
    "answer_id" : 10453977,
    "question_id" : 4778113,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>SHA1's answer did it for me: after updating to the latest sdk/adt, my project refused to build an apk; unchecking the option resolved the issue. </p>\n\n<p>I don't know if the update checked this, or if it was checked before but the new adt screwed things up, but things work again now :)</p>\n"
