    "question_id" : 4778113,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I tried all the above solutions. but it didn't work.</p>\n\n<p>The solution was to restart eclipse !!!!!!!</p>\n\n<p>hope this will help someone :)</p>\n"
